{"tid":2036846,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"中國STEAM：你不能在晚上10點與早上8點間玩遊戲，請休息","createTime":"2020-05-26T16:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T02:25:15.000Z","uid":212274,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"69f5e2db2faa6e37a4d69fb6a39f3ca4d8159f78","tid":2036846,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/26/99/7936197.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F99%2F7936197.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=6f631d67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中國版Steam「蒸汽平台」自2018年與中國在地遊戲商「完美世界」的合作公開以來，都只見消息，不見本體。日前一家外媒取得了中國版Steam的Alpha測試版，除了不意外地有健康警告、限制遊玩時間外，還可能會有用戶端審查，包括頭像與ID的露出等，非常符合中國目前對遊戲內容的監管政策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://根據Win.GG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%A0%B9%E6%93%9AWin.GG&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA1SbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=d09d3772\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">根據Win.GG</a>報導，目前的Alpha版基本上就是改自Steam用戶端平台介面，不過在啟動任何遊戲前都會看到一則「健康遊戲忠告」，內容大致是「抵制不良遊戲，拒絕盜版，沈迷遊戲傷身」等訊息，與之前中國網友挖出的未成年防沈迷警語如出一轍，只是是英文版本。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/26/99/7935848.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F99%2F7935848.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=bc94a94b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外，<a href=\"http://Win.GG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FWin.GG&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA1SbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=a9f462f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Win.GG</a>進一步又發現，Steam的用戶頭像都被改成官方預設的「？」，名稱都一律變成Steam ID。這意味著頭像與ID可能都得經過官方審查，也有可能與中國目前力推的實名制有關。<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2020/05/26/99/7935846.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2020%2F05%2F26%2F99%2F7935846.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050&h=d908c177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n接著在他們嘗試啟動《CS:GO》時，居然出現「你不能在晚上10點與早上8點間玩遊戲，請休息」的訊息。<a href=\"http://雖然Win.GG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E9%9B%96%E7%84%B6Win.GG&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA1SbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=60a5223f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">雖然Win.GG</a>當時是在允許的時間啟動遊戲，但可能是系統默認為中國時區，所以被拒於門外，另一款《DotA 2》也同樣啟動失敗。<br />\n<img src=\"https://truth.bahamut.com.tw/s01/202005/5e50aae396fe9794dc9267fc9e17c512.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftruth.bahamut.com.tw%2Fs01%2F202005%2F5e50aae396fe9794dc9267fc9e17c512.JPG&h=894aa3d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有趣的是，《CS:GO》、《DotA 2》在中國的代理商都是完美世界，所以這些遊戲早以預埋了限制系統。而當他們開啟其他遊戲時，還是可以正常運行。<br />\n<br />\nSteam最近因為一連串的「辱華風波」也遭受波及，雖然中國網友檯面上憤恨不平，但真正的玩家都知道，自己整天翻牆跨區，為的都是享受到最原始、無和諧內容，現在除了要抵擋小粉紅的攻勢外，還得擔心「國行版」Steam的正式實施。目前Valve都沒有對外公開相關訊息，屆時是否真的能嚴格限制中國玩家「出國遊玩」，只能等待中國版本正式上線了。"},{"pid":"1e7d6d7ce5c20e46e886dec3d9ca0ac7df8e5090","tid":2036846,"uid":273593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果5.27失敗 有plan B</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2b90e7db220b7453ae7f2b875bed9c71b914a23","tid":2036846,"uid":212274,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:50:47.000Z","msg":"想做毒撚要問下國家先<br />\n只能在國家許可時段做part time毒撚，好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a68fddf08f4732111eb32ad4f253b1ef7613657","tid":2036846,"uid":271759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b00b45d8756b8e62c49c13100175e19b9567310","tid":2036846,"uid":26715,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:22:38.000Z","msg":"咪撚笑， 好快到香港"},{"pid":"279eb0980925a50065a2b150775c40ed0b9d28bd","tid":2036846,"uid":286792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T17:35:38.000Z","msg":"感謝黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f6fe4b452e08b8b4e5115ae0aef176cd0290b59","tid":2036846,"uid":222795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T20:43:23.000Z","msg":"自由到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d96bb078f93d7c3d476eb4640ae24d344921e28","tid":2036846,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T02:25:15.000Z","msg":"夜收工既人連打機既時間都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"1e7d6d7ce5c20e46e886dec3d9ca0ac7df8e5090","tid":2036846,"uid":273593,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T16:50:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">如果5.27失敗 有plan B</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2036797\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2036797</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}}